formThreeBId.notesToCertificate: Note 1 : Amount shown in Deposit during the period means amount received from customers and paid if there is excess received because of sanction of bank loan and  due to cancellation of unit. Note 2. Since there is Single RERA account without splitting amount received from customer in to retention and current account therefore we were calculating cumulative withdrawn amount by deducting closing bank balance from total amount received from customers for the project in quarterly returns filed earlier which also includes the portion of 30% of Gross Receipts from customers which are not required to be deposited in designated account. In current quarter the same have been ractified. Note 3 : As per the regulations, the AFS is to be entered when the amount is received by the promoter exceeds 10% of the Unit Consideration however we observed in fewer cases there has been delay in entering to the AFS but the same is regularised after that by executing either AFS or sale deed except for 3 Units. Note 4 : Project loan taken of the property is fully paid on 28/12/2020 vide NOC received from the bank and charge on Project Mortgage loan taken is released on  30/01/2021 vide RR No. 1798 dated 30/01/21 at SRO, Ahmedabad -2 Vadaj.
